divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the car driving. I first noticed the object because of the lights, but i thought it was just a reflection. Then I got closer and i realized it was an UFO. I thought it was a kite at first, because it was moving as if it were tied to something. It had a choreographed movement. It would spin, dart for left to right, do a barrell roll, dive then come back up to where it started and begin again. During the sighting, i felt happy and curious, but I was trimbeling a bit. After the sighting,I was very scared and shakey, i was worried about my safety. I lost sight of the object, because i drove closer then I looked away and i never saw it again after that.
Summary: Triangle, about the size of a car, red and blue lights
